The red light filled his face like the bright sun, and the loud cry was like the sound of thunder drumming.
Humpy temples. The belly rumbles like thunders.

In your sleep, you suddenly remember the grievances of your previous life. After waking up and recalling the things in your dream, you find that everything has turned into a mysterious text, which helps you comprehend a long-lost ultimate skill in the Jianghu.
While playing with companions, I was accidentally shot in the eye by a slingshot and blinded, but accidentally awakened an talent with strong hearing no less than ordinary people.
I accidentally fell off a cliff and my legs were crippled. I also accidentally ate unknown wild fruits, but since then I have understood everything. I have extraordinary wisdom.

The companion star Beta was considered an ominous person. Because his parents died early, he suffered a lot of bullying. In a rage, he went into the deep mountains, but accidentally broke into the cave mansion of an immortal and comprehended the fateful ultimate skill [Destruction].

Because of extraordinary appearance, I have been loved by people since childhood. , Born with an appearance beyond the mundane world, I have been the darling of neighbors and passersby since childhood, and after adulthood I look like a celestial being.

The appearance is different from ordinary people and is despised, but later a wandering Taoist saw you and was shocked as a celestial being, so he taught you the unique internal skills, hoping that you will remember him when you achieve great achievements in the future.
Your talent continued to grow. There was no bottleneck for you in learning martial arts.

A big ape carried you away into the mountains and woods. After a few years,you were found by a stream and brought back. Since then you became well versed in animal’s language and thus close to animals.

Born stupid, learning is extremely slow and often despised by others. Later, I abandoned literature and studied martial arts, but found that I could take the initiative in actual combat and maneuver freely.
In a cold snowy season,you looked heathy,radiant,and refreshed.
In a burning hot season,you felt comfortable and refreshed.
When I was born, there was a faint purple snake-shaped birthmark on my face, which became clearer and clearer with age.

【<TDName>[Cold poison latent disease]</> The cold state occurs 10 times to cause cold poison latent disease. Treatment: Hospital, Hot Spring, Self-Healing in Meridians】

Humph! Of course I am human! Forget it, I will not be the same as you juniors.\\nI am <TDName>[Tiansheng Lao]</>, you call me <TDName>[Tian Lao]</>.\\n You can hear my voice because my <TDName>[Chuan Yin Ru Mi]</> has been achieved. It is not difficult to convey sound to you in this place.

I have traveled all over the world for hundreds of years. I have countless enemies under my hands. If our relationship is known in advance, I'm afraid I'll have to wait for hundreds of years again?\\nYou only need to know that this place is called <TDName>[Da Huang Jie]</>, which is where you and I are trapped. The most important thing now is that you need to strengthen your strength as soon as possible to take the position of <TDName>[Wulin Alliance Lord]</>. I'll tell you how to help me get rid of trouble when the time comes.

Of course, I will not let you suffer losses. All the martial arts in this <TDName>[Da Huang Jie]</> are what I have learned. I just hope that you can achieve hegemony as soon as possible. This is a win-win situation for you and me.
<TDName>[Tian Shu Bao Dian]</> is the crystallization of my heart and mind. Its content will gradually emerge as you gain experience.
It seems that this can only be the case, but how come this <TDName>[Da Huang Jie]</> is so small?

Small? \\n......\\nForget it, it seems that too much time has passed and you have forgotten your instinct. Boy, you need to remember: as <TDName>[Geng Fu]</>, when your strength recovers, you will naturally understand many mysteries in this world.
So what should I do now?

............\\nIt seems that you really forgot a lot. I still have a little time to help you for the time being.\\nEach plot in this <TDName>[Da Huang Jie]</> has a <TDName>[Regional Experience]</>. Complete the experience of this plot first.
Very good! Your skills and wisdom are much better than I imagined! \\nFollow this step, and there is hope for me to get rid of trouble when the time comes! Hahaha.

Open the <TDName>[Fei Ge Chuan Shu]</>, and you will naturally see how to develop the <TDName>[Da Huang Jie]</>. Each area of <TDName>[Da Huang Jie]</> has unique resources.\\nMake good use of these resources to accelerate your growth. However, the hearts of people in the rivers and lakes are complicated, and you should be careful to deal with them in your daily life.\\nIn addition, if you have a lot of money, you can also find <TDName>[merchant ships]</> to develop new plots.
Stop! Don't go further into the open sea! This is very dangerous!
What’s out there in the sea? !!
Why? Looks calm enough to me.
Go back first, the time is not ripe yet! I will tell you everything when the time comes!
I need to see for myself what is out there.
Ah, it's good for young people to suffer a little.

As the world expands, the forces of <TDName>[Da Huang Jie]</> will also increase. Without enough strength, it is impossible to deal with a more complex environment in the rivers and lakes. The top priority is to first join a sect to accumulate strength, and then gradually plot the throne of <TDName>[Wulin Alliance Lord]</>.
How can I join a sect?
The <TDName>[Bulletin Board]</> outside each sect's mountain gate will write the requirements for accepting disciples. You can go there to see if you meet the requirements.

Please note! New expanded plots will appear as <TDName>[bandits]</>. They are all defeated people in the rivers and lakes. Eliminating them can gain fame in the rivers and lakes. But remember to demolish their huts and cages, otherwise there will still be villains coming here to make trouble.
What if I’m no match for them?
Hire bodyguards and set traps. Sometimes avoiding the edge is also a good choice. Wait until your strength is strong or you have built your own power, and ordinary bandits will not be feared.
What else do you want to know about?
How can I join a sect?
Each sect's mountain gate has a bulletin board. You can go see if you meet the conditions to enter the door. But others may not necessarily value you~~
Do you know where the treasures are?
Horses like to eat grass, monkeys like to eat pine nuts or plums, martens and snakes like to eat meat and eggs, and eagles like to eat meat.
When will the Wulin Conference be held?

As long as there is an area where the Wulin Conference is held, it will be held after a period of time. I look forward to it~~ If you can become the leader of Wulin, you can really do whatever you want, hahaha.
For minor injuries, self-gasification can be used for treatment. If the injury is too serious, you can only go to the infirmary for treatment, but their charges are quite expensive...

Trading, helping others complete commission tasks, or doing odd jobs in major stores. However, no matter how, it is not as fast as doing extraordinary things, haha, without night grass horses will not grow fat!
How can you be invincible in the world?

Hehehe~ There is no real invincibility in this world~ You can improve your strength by collecting secret skills, inner strength, abilities and equipment, but only by combining them properly can you truly become powerful.
I heard that you can comprehend advanced light skills at Falcon Terrace and Mirror Lake Shilin.
You can purchase various status-increasing foods on the wine rack in the tavern, and praying for rain and snow in the City Temple can also increase the cold.
How to learn martial arts from the sect?

The bookshelves in the practice room can purchase the unique skills and internal skills of this sect. When your prestige in this sect reaches a certain height, you can take these martial arts at will.

Challenging a person with a higher position or completing the entrusted task of a member of the sect can increase the prestige of the sect. When the prestige meets the requirements of the next position, you can find the head of the sect for job promotion evaluation
Execute more sect orders, or submit materials to the warehouse.
What do you do in the practice room?

My heaviest daily work is to check various equipment in the practice room, such as [wooden men] and [bookshelves]. Once any problems are found, they will be repaired and replaced immediately to ensure that they are in the best condition and ready for the disciples at any time.
What do you do in the warehouse?

I have been in charge of warehouse management for a long time. My main daily work is to register the incoming and outgoing of various materials of the sect, to ensure that funds and materials can be properly kept for use by the disciples of the sect.
What do you do in prison?

Although I am not proficient in martial arts, I have rich experience in guarding and interrogating prisoners. The head of the sect trusts my work very much. All key prisoners are under my responsibility. I am mainly responsible for guarding the [prison]. Those who violate the rules of the sect or provoke this sect are under my unified supervision.
What do you do in the tavern?

Ensure that all facilities in the tavern operate normally every day, check whether the wine and food on the [wine rack] are complete, how the income of the [wine table] is, and listen to the drunken words of the knights. My ideal is to run a good tavern and provide customers with a comfortable environment.
What do you do in the stables?

I make money by selling horses in [horse stalls] and post stations. There are also some treasures I have collected in the counter, and some miscellaneous goods are sold in the sundry cabinet. If there is no important business, I will usually stay here.
Do you know what animals like to eat?

I only know some: [horses] like to eat mixed grass, [eagles] like to eat meat chunks, [monkeys] like to eat pine nuts and plums, [snakes] and [martens] like to eat meat chunks and eggs, and [chickens] like Eat all kinds of insects.
What do you do in the blacksmith shop?

I make money by selling forged weapons and hidden weapons on the [weapon rack]. If I have enough materials, I will make weapons. I have devoted my life to refining the art of alchemy and metallurgy, and have cast many magic weapons and sharp tools that are spread throughout the rivers and lakes.
What do you do in the cloth village?

I make money by selling hats, clothes and trousers woven on the [clothing rack]. If I have enough materials, I will weave better clothes. What I like most in my life is to make a peerless outfit for the masters, so that they can be awe-inspiring and walk the rivers and lakes.
What do you do at the hot spring?

I make money by operating the [hot spring]. The reason for opening the hot spring is simple. I just hope that more people can experience the wonderful use of the hot spring and get a pleasant mood here.
What do you do at Langya Pavilion?

I make money by selling various organs on the [organ rack]. Those in the rivers and lakes who want to decorate their residences, hunt traps, or hide their shapes will take care of my business. This is my life.
What do you do in the infirmary?

I make money by treating patients on the [sickbed] and selling elixir on the [medicine rack]. When I have nothing to do, I will practice alchemy and cultivate my body. Those in the martial arts world come to see a doctor, I never ask for names and origins, as long as I can treat, I will do my best. This is also the foundation of my medical ethics.
Lie down on the sickbed quickly, and I will come to see your symptoms.
What do you do in the music building?
The reason for opening the music building is simple. I just hope that more people can appreciate the charm of music, drink and listen to the piano here to eliminate fatigue. Isn't it fast?
What do you do in the countryside?

My ancestors were all farmers and were quite good at planting various products. I just look at how the crops grown in the [fields] are growing every day. Those in the rivers and lakes who need herbs will also come to purchase them.
